<html>

<head>
  <title>Express</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
</head>

<body>

  <h1>Is <b>"{{ s }}"</b> in the Bible?</h1>
  <p>Of these words, {{ nInTheBible }} are in the Bible, and {{ nNotInTheBible }} are not.</p>
  <p>This sentence is {{ (nInTheBible/(nInTheBible+nNotInTheBible)*100)|round(1) }}% Bibular.</p>
  <ul>
    {% for res in results %}
      {% if res[0] %}
        <li>
          <b>{{ res[1] }}</b> : Book {{ res[0].book_name }} Chapter {{ res[0].chapter }} Verse {{ res[0].verse }}
        </li>
      {% else %}
        <li>
          <b>{{ res[1] }}</b> is not in the Bible
        </li>
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}

  </ul>

</body>

</html>
